## Design principles (for skill maintainers)
 
This skill was built with the following explicit constraints:
 
- **Evidence taxonomy over confident assertion** — every material claim is
  classified as Direct, Inferred, Estimated, or Speculative
- **Conservative status anchoring** — when in doubt, go more cautious
- **Anti-overclaiming** — no percentages without numbers, no timelines without dates,
  no progress without evidence
- **Honesty over polish** — gaps and weak evidence are surfaced, not smoothed
- **No individual attribution** — roles only, never names
- **No Scrum bleed** — sprint language only when the input supports it
- **Lean project instructions** — skill logic stays in files, not in Project setup
 
